# room-connect — Project Overview

room-connect is an **interactive web-based 3D connectivity editor and rendering pipeline**. It lets users load GLTF/GLB 3D scenes, draw axis-aligned bounding box volumes to define walkable areas, detect objects with OOBBs, place cameras, and render views via Blender Cycles.

## High-level features

1. **Volume Connectivity**: Draw, translate, scale AABB volumes; define connectivity; export graph JSON.
2. **Object Detection**: Filter scene meshes by name, compute OOBBs, cull overlapping boxes, export object JSON.
3. **Rendering**: Place cameras manually (Place at View), render from all cameras via Blender Cycles (backend), override lighting with brightness control, export ZIP of renders + depthmaps + .blend files + camera intrinsics/extrinsics.

